## What Is Wazuh?
Wazuh is a free open source SIEM platform.

It has three parts:

| Part | Purpose | Location |
|---|---|---|
| Wazuh Agent | Collects logs from devices | Installed on each device |
| Wazuh Server | Receives and analyzes logs | Central server |
| Wazuh Dashboard | Visual interface | Accessed via browser |

Think of it like a hospital:
- Agent = Nurse collecting patient data
- Server = Doctor analyzing the data
- Dashboard = Screen showing results

---

## What Is A Wazuh Agent?
A small program installed on each device that:
- Watches everything happening on that device
- Collects logs
- Sends them to Wazuh Server every few seconds

Every unmonitored device = blind spot for attackers.
In real companies — agents are deployed to every single device.

