## Common Mistakes

- ❌ Using number zero (0) instead of capital letter O in commands
- ❌ Using dash (-) instead of dot (.) in filenames
- ❌ Running PowerShell without Administrator privileges
- ❌ Forgetting to open firewall ports 1514 and 1515
- ❌ Installing agent on same machine as manager — they conflict
- ❌ Assuming one scan or check covers everything

